{
  "stem": "7069.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's hieroglyphics that, I think they tried to imitate, somehow, the Hebrew writing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the letters are supposed to represent-- are representing-- J-U-D-E, which is the word for Jew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so this is made out of fine cloth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And with it came the order that this has to be sewn on your left side of whatever outer garment you wear, in tight stitches, like one millimeter apart from each other.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And now we, we were stopped on the streets, sometimes to see and checked if these stitches are not-- I know of a person that had a corner loose.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And some eyewitnesses saw that he was stopped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Gestapo guy grabbed the corner, tore the star off, and another Gestapo guy grabbed the guy by the neck and shoved him into the waiting black limousine there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So another--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not I, a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this man-- I knew the person that it happened to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this person was taken away and was never seen again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, this was a situation-- you're talking about danger and being frightened-- a loose corner of this dumb star could cost you your life, as it did in this case, and in many other cases I know, too.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exactly, it's a ridiculous thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you don't know, and you are now concerned, maybe yeah-- this is what my mother said, you know something, as much as I hate this thing, I am glad about it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This at least now keeps you home and out of danger, because I don't think you dare to go after curfew in a place with this thing.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
